Title: Message To New Members
Author: CareersNG_Admin
Date: Sat Jul 07, 2007 5:54 pm
Forum: Announcement
Content: Welcome to CareersNG Forum.
CareersNG is a website dedicated to providing needfull advice/help and relevant information and technology to improve people in their career. Our focus is on Nigerians and friends of Nigeria.
Career to us simply means;
-What you do.
-What you do to earn leaving(What puts bread on your table).
-What you regualrly and periodically devote to be doing in life.
Its obvious that a lot of Nigerians have challenges with their careers. A lot of people dont even have a job or own a bussiness, less building up their careers. A lot dont even know the best job or profession that suites their person. A lot need relevant information to handle their income/finance. A lot need encouragement, motivation and self confidence to forge ahead and achieve their goals. A lot need to get advice from people who have gone ahead of them. etc

Enjoy..
